data.description: Welcome to your spacious 2-story loving townhome. This beautiful space has 3 bedrooms and 2 ½ baths. On the first floor, you have your 2 living room areas, ½ bath, laundry space, a fireplace for your cozy moments, 2 eating areas, and a large kitchen with plenty of counter space which includes a breakfast bar. Some of the features you will notice throughout your home will be your beautiful kitchen backsplash, Corian counters, hardwood flooring, ceramic tile, neutral paints, double-paned windows, and more. All bedrooms are upstairs and your primary bedroom includes its own bathroom, vanity area, and 2 large closets. The large fenced patio, which is enclosed and covered, has plenty of room for your gardening. The carport is directly behind the townhome which also includes an extra storage room. The location of your home is near to many major intersections for easy access to all areas of Houston. Come see your home today!
